      <title>Re: Class issues lists – Updated Version (Wizard)</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=wizardbalance&amp;message.id=2388#M2388</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff00ff&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Wizard&lt;/STRONG&gt; - &lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;List Update scheduled for&amp;nbsp;03/04/05&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;1) &lt;STRONG&gt;Short to Medium term damage -&lt;/STRONG&gt; &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;This will most likely be considered as part of the class Re-Envision process.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
